@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mxjtio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp + 0.81)
    tmp = 0.45
    v0 = (wp.exp(v2) - ((tmp + 0.18 * v1 + 0.13) - (v2 + 0.68 - v2 + 0.07)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.44 - v1 + 0.86)) - wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.39)))
    data[tid] = v0
